{% doc %}
  Bundle Sticky Buy Box
  
  This snippet displays the sticky buy box on the build bundle page.

  Main functionalities:
  - Shows the products added to the bundle and a pricing summary.
  - Displays the checkout button for completing the purchase.
  - Shows an empty cart message when there are no products in the bundle.
  - Allows users to add or remove products from the bundle.
  - Provides the button to add the bundle to the cart.

  All these elements work together to create a cohesive and intuitive shopping experience.
{% enddoc %}

